part12
Extracting data from XML responses and chaining requests
Extracting data from responses and chaining requests

WS.verifyElementText(response, 'ListOfCountryNamesByNameResponse.ListOfCountryNamesByNameResult.tCountryCodeAndName[0].sISOCode', 'AX')

http://webservices.oorsprong.org/webs...

Sample Code

String xml1 = response1.responseBodyContent

def dataValue= new XmlSlurper().parseText(xml1)

def countryCode = dataValue.ListOfCountryNamesByNameResult.tCountryCodeAndName[2].sISOCode.text()

GlobalVariable.name = countryCode

